english: this is a small bird with a black, grey and white pattern on its wings and tail, a yellow throat and a black and yellow belly.

indo: burung hitam pekat berukuran sedang hingga besar, dengan paruh hitam agak melengkung, dan kaki berwarna hitam.

english: this is a small bird, with a yellow chest, green crown and nape, with a point black bill.

english: this bird is grey with black and white on its wings and has a very short beak.

english: this bird has a white breast, a tan wing, and a black foot

english: this is a medium sized multi-colored bird with a very long grey pointed beak, the head and wings are bluish grey, there are very large white check patches, the breast is a rusty brown, and the belly is white with a grey border.

english: this bird has a bunch of feathers on it's crown, and a back that is brown with white spots.

english: a white body is covered with yellow and green downward pointing feathers on the breast.

english: this bird has a white underbelly and a mixture between a black and green wing.
indo: burung ini mempunyai perut bagian bawah berwarna putih dan sayap campuran antara warna hitam dan hijau.

english: this colorful bird has a blue tail and wings, blue head and a brown throat and breast, while the abdomen is gray.
indo: Burung berwarna-warni ini memiliki ekor dan sayap berwarna biru, kepala berwarna biru, serta tenggorokan dan dada berwarna coklat, sedangkan bagian perutnya berwarna abu-abu.

english: very round brown bird with gray striped belly, short wings and straight, small brown beak.
indo: burung berwarna coklat sangat bulat dengan perut bergaris abu-abu, sayap pendek dan lurus, paruh kecil berwarna coklat.

english: this bird has a blakc crown, a long black bill, and two black webbed feet
indo: burung ini mempunyai mahkota berwarna hitam, paruh panjang berwarna hitam, dan dua kaki berselaput hitam

english: short beaked, black and yellow bird with long tail and no neck.
indo: Burung berparuh pendek, berwarna hitam kuning, berekor panjang dan tidak berleher.
